Package com.iontrading.mkv.helper

Interface MkvSupplyProxy

  • All Superinterfaces:
    MkvSupply
    @Keep
@KeepPublicClassMemberNames
public interface MkvSupplyProxy
extends MkvSupply
    This interface defines a common set of operations for proxying a Class of java objects into a MkvSupply interface and viceversa.

    • Method Summary
